                                    "MCLAREN FORMULA 1", "ASTON MARTIN ARAMCO", "ALPINE F1 TEAM",
                                    "WILLIAMS RACING", "HAAS F1 TEAM", "STAKE KICK SAUBER", "VISA CASH APP RB"
